馬友友爲多部电影音乐配樂，其中包括[[布萊德·彼特|布萊德·彼特]]主演的電影《[[西藏七年_(电影)|西藏七年]]》，[[李安|李安]]导演的《[[卧虎藏龙|卧虎藏龙]]》等。

1999年2月，[[美國|美國]][[紐約市|紐約市]]將[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]東46街與[[第五大道|第五大道]]交叉口的路牌，暫時性地換成「馬友友路」（Yo-Yo Ma Way）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-88893973.html |title=N.Y. Doles Out Honorary Street Names |access-date=2007-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421225349/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-88893973.html |archive-date=2016-04-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2021年3月，馬友友在美國[[麻薩諸塞州|麻州]][[皮茨菲尔德_(马萨诸塞州)|皮茨菲爾德]]一間社區學院，接種第二劑[[2019冠状病毒病疫苗|COVID-19疫苗]]後即席演奏大提琴，在場人士報以熱烈掌聲。網民讚許馬友友透過音樂撫慰人心<ref>{{cite web|title=Yo-Yo Ma Gives a Surprise Concert at Vaccination Site|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/14/world/yo-yo-ma-berkshire-community-college.html|author=Jennifer Jett|date=2021-03-14|publisher=The New York Times|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519145134/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/03/14/world/yo-yo-ma-berkshire-community-college.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Yo-Yo Ma played a surprise concert for a clinic during his post-vaccination waiting period|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/2021/03/14/yo-yo-ma-vaccine-concert|author=Paulina Firozi|date=2021-03-14|publisher=Washington Post|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317100113/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/2021/03/14/yo-yo-ma-vaccine-concert/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cellist Yo-Yo Ma stuns with impromptu performance of 'Ave Maria' at vaccine site|url=https://www.today.com/popculture/cellist-yo-yo-ma-stuns-impromptu-performance-ave-maria-vaccine-t211717|author=Ronnie Koenig|date=2021-03-14|publisher=Today.com|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331122054/https://www.today.com/popculture/cellist-yo-yo-ma-stuns-impromptu-performance-ave-maria-vaccine-t211717|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Yo-Yo Ma celebrates 2nd COVID-19 shot by transforming vaccination clinic into concert hall|url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/yo-yo-ma-celebrates-2nd-covid-19-shot/story?id=76445576|author=Arielle Mitropoulos|date=2021-03-14|publisher=ABC News|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414133949/https://abcnews.go.com/US/yo-yo-ma-celebrates-2nd-covid-19-shot/story?id=76445576|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

